		<h3 class="topfeatures">Kill.Node Features:</h3>
		<p>Utilizing SVG graphics generated by RaphaÃ«l &amp; browser-based geo-location, players can see those near them and attempt to "kill" each other for points. <strong >NOTE: We <span class="red">strongly recommend <a href="http://www.google.com/chrome">Chrome</a> on the desktop</span> for it's superior performance with JavaScript and SVG rendering. Also important to know, this application collects your location (only after requesting permission through the browser) but does not publicly display that in relation to anybody's user data.</strong></p>
		<p>The goal is to kill before you are killed - score points by eliminating targets near you, lose points if someone gets you first.</p>


		<form class="login"action="/sessions" method="POST">
		  <fieldset>
		    <legend>Login:</legend>
		    
		    <% if (params.login_errors && params.login_errors.length > 0) { %>
		      <ul class="errors">
		        <% for (i = 0; i < params.login_errors.length; i++) { %>
		          <li><%= params.login_errors[i] %></li>
		        <% } %>
		      </ul>
		    <% } %>
		    
				<a name="login" ></a>
		    <ol>
		      <li>
		        <label for="user_username">Username</label>
		        <input type="text" name="username" value="<%= params.login_username || "" %>">
		      </li>
		      <li>
		        <label for="user_password">Password</label>
		        <input type="password" name="password" value="">
		      </li>
		      <li>			
		        <input type="submit" value="Login" />
		      </li>
		    </ol>
		  </fieldset>
		</form>
		
		<form class="signup" action="/users" method="POST">
		  <fieldset>
		    <legend>Signup to play:</legend>

		    <% if (params.user_errors && params.user_errors.length > 0) { %>
		      <ul class="errors">
		        <% for (i = 0; i < params.user_errors.length; i++) { %>
		          <li><%= params.user_errors[i] %></li>
		        <% } %>
		      </ul>
		    <% } %>

		    <ol>
			    <li>
			      <label for="user_username">Username</label>
			      <input type="text" name="user_username" value="<%= params.user_username || "" %>">
			    </li>
			    <li>
			      <label for="user_email">E-mail Address</label>
			      <input type="text" name="user_email" value="<%= params.user_email || "" %>">
			    </li>
			    <li>
			      <label for="user_password">Password</label>
			      <input type="password" name="user_password" value="<%= params.user_password || "" %>">
			    </li>
			    <li>
			      <label for="user_password_confirmation">Password Confirmation</label>
			      <input type="password" name="user_password_confirmation" value="<%= params.user_password_confirmation || "" %>">
			    </li>
			    <li>
			      <input class="btn" type="submit" value="Register!" />
			    </li>
				</ol>
		  </fieldset>
		</form>

		<br style="clear: both;" />
